IUpdate Interface

Definition

The set of configurations that can be updated for all endpoint irrespective of their type (Azure, external, nested profile).

In this Article

public interface IUpdate : Microsoft.Azure.Management.ResourceManager.Fluent.Core.ChildResourceActions.ISettable<Microsoft.Azure.Management.TrafficManager.Fluent.TrafficManagerProfile.Update.IUpdate>, Microsoft.Azure.Management.TrafficManager.Fluent.TrafficManagerEndpoint.Update.IWithRoutingPriority, Microsoft.Azure.Management.TrafficManager.Fluent.TrafficManagerEndpoint.Update.IWithRoutingWeight, Microsoft.Azure.Management.TrafficManager.Fluent.TrafficManagerEndpoint.Update.IWithTrafficDisabledOrEnabled
